  <summary date="2017-10-19T04:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">Protecting Airport Communities from Particle Emissions Act 

This bill directs the Federal Aviation Administration (FAA) to report on ultrafine particles and their health impacts for communities around the 20 largest U.S. airports. The FAA must coordinate with the Environmental Protection Agency, the Department of Health and Human Services, and others.</summary>
